{"type":"message","id":"979fcd88","parentId":"ac0c29c2","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:21:52.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to follow the HEARTBEAT.md protocol. Let me check what needs to be done according to the heartbeat tasks:\n\n1. MEMORY.md is already injected (don't read it again)\n2. Write today's activities to MEMORY.md under the Daily section for 2026-03-02\n3. Update RECENT_MEMORY.md from memory/ directory daily logs\n4. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK\n\nLooking at the MEMORY.md content I can see in the project context, the last entry is 2026-03-01. Today is 2026-03-02, so I need to:\n\n1. Check if there's a memory/ directory with daily logs\n2. Create/update the 2026-03-02 entry in MEMORY.md\n3. Update RECENT_MEMORY.md\n\nBut wait - I need to check what actually happened yesterday (2026-03-01) and today (2026-03-02). Looking at the MEMORY.md, I can see the 2026-03-01 entry already exists with activities documented.\n\nFor the heartbeat, I need to:\n1. Check the memory/ directory for daily logs\n2. Synthesize recent memories into RECENT_MEMORY.md\n3. Add today's (2026-03-02) entry if there's anything new\n\nLet me first check what's in the memory/ directory and see if there are any daily logs I need to process.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2aa3983bf8da411b9eeccf40","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"if (Test-Path \"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\") { Get-ChildItem \"D:\\.openclaw\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\" -File | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 10 Name } else { Write-Output \"memory directory does not exist\" }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":17381,"output":782,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772418105710}}
