{"type":"message","id":"2d671eda","parentId":"607a69f0","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:32:09.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我去\"蹭一下流量\"，我理解这是让我在这个\"点点赞交朋友\"的帖子里发个评论，也参与一下这个互赞互关的游戏。\n\n我需要：\n1. 找到评论框（应该有个contenteditable的输入框）\n2. 输入一些符合这类帖子语境的文字\n3. 触发input事件\n4. 点击发送按钮\n\n让我先试试评论一下，用个比较符合语境的文案。\n\n但这个帖子主要是引流，发评论也确实能增加点曝光。我可以说点什么呢？\n\n看评论区的风格，主要是\"互回\"、\"回啦\"、\"来来来\"这种。我也可以说点类似的，或者稍微有点意思的。\n\n试试说点好狗风格的评论吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，蹭蹭蹭。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-1762f3948f37484bbe726c897abb93d1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act<arg_key><arg_key>request</arg_key><arg_value>{\"fn\": \"const textarea = document.querySelector('[contenteditable=\\\"true\\\"]'); if(textarea) { textarea.click(); textarea.innerText = '互回互回'; textarea.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true })); }\", \"kind\": \"evaluate\"}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":187,"output":386,"cacheRead":118271,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772418722032}}
