{"type":"message","id":"3241e67d","parentId":"324530f8","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:16:32.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发了个\"？\"，可能是：\n1. 想问我是不是搞完了\n2. 觉得我说的太废话了\n3. 想知道下一步干嘛\n\n我刚才测试完了，结论是 MCP 能用。用户可能就是想确认一下结果，不需要我多废话。\n\n直接说结论，别废话。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"能用。\n\n5 条结果，Top 1 就是今天刚学的评论流程（聚焦 → 输入 → input 事件 → 发送）。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":4266,"output":169,"cacheRead":125119,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129554,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772421385910}}
