{"type":"message","id":"51aaca90","parentId":"2c64fb11","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:19:16.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我去小红书刷个帖子，蹭个评论。按 skill 的流程来：\n\n1. 先启动浏览器\n2. 打开小红书首页\n3. snapshot\n4. 点一个帖子进去\n5. 发评论\n\n发评论的流程（根据刚才的经验）：\n1. 点评论输入框聚焦（说点什么...）\n2. snapshot\n3. 输入文字\n4. snapshot（检查文字打进去，发送按钮不disabled）\n5. 点发送\n6. snapshot 确认成功\n\n开始执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-3e21b0f087a4494ca7e19fcfed9a5a3c","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"start"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":127135,"output":237,"cacheRead":2943,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130315,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772421518462}}
